{{Spanish name|Peralta|Álvarez}}
'''Sebelio Peralta Álvarez''' (September 19, 1939 &ndash; November 19, 2014) was a [[Roman Catholic]] bishop.

Ordained to the priesthood in 1964, Peralta Álvarez was named auxiliary bishop of the Roman Catholic Diocese of [[Villarrica, Paraguay|Villarrica]], [[Paraguay]] in 1979. He was then named bishop of the Diocese of Villerrica del Espíritu Santo in 1990. In 2008, he was named bishop of the Roman Catholic Diocese of San Lorenzo.<ref>[http://www.catholic-hierarchy.org/bishop/bpeal.html Sebelio Peralta Alvarez]</ref>

