*[[Parker Jacobs]] as John Cavanaugh
*[[Danny Cooksey]] as Kevin Cavanaugh
*[[Art Carney]] appeared in three episodes as Pop's younger brother, Jimmy "The Weasel" Cavanaugh.<ref name="Campbell" />

